sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant Server

    User->>Browser: Opens the web page
    Browser->>Server: Sends POST request to create SPA
    Server-->>Browser: Returns confirmation and initial HTML
    Browser->>Server: Requests CSS and JavaScript files
    Server-->>Browser: Returns CSS and JavaScript files
    Browser->>Browser: Renders the initial page
    User->>Browser: Interacts with the page (clicks a link)
    Browser->>Server: Requests necessary data (AJAX)
    Server-->>Browser: Returns data in JSON format
    Browser->>Browser: Updates the view with the new data
